'From Pharo3.0 of 18 March 2013 [Latest update: #30858] on 4 October 2014 at 8:57:22.172008 pm'!Object subclass: #PatrolCouple	instanceVariableNames: 'patrol sniper'	classVariableNames: ''	poolDictionaries: ''	category: 'BotArena'!!PatrolCouple commentStamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:15' prior: 0!A PatrolCouple is a container for robots to patrol.Instance Variables	patrol:		<Object>	sniper:		<Object>patrol	- xxxxxsniper	- xxxxx!!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:15'!sniper: aRobot "Asigna un robot a sniper" sniper := aRobot.! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:32'!reset  "Ambos robots se posicionan enfrentados a distancia 5 uno del otro (uno mira al    south y el otro al north, uno de ellos posicionado en 20@20"  self patrol    north;    position: (20@30).  self sniper    south;    position: (20@25).! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:15'!patrol: aRobot  "Asigna un robot a patrol"   patrol := aRobot.! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:33'!regularPatrol  "patrol hace un cuadrado de lado 10 rotado 45 grados alrededor de sniper,    sniper en el centro gira en sentido de las agujas del reloj."  self patrol rotatedSquareOfSize: 10 at: ((self sniper position x - 10)@(self sniper position y)).  4 timesRepeat: [self sniper rotateRight: 90]! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:40'!doTheRegularPatrolTrace  "Similar a doTheRegularPatrol pero cada robot deja un trazo en la arena con  el brush"  5 timesRepeat: [    (self patrol canDoRegularPatrol) & (self sniper battery charge >= 9)      ifTrue: [ self patrol north. self regularPatrol ]  ]! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:15'!sniper  "Retorna un sniper"  ^ sniper! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:15'!patrol: aPatrol sniper: aSniper  "Asigna un patrol y un sniper"  self    patrol: aPatrol;    sniper: aSniper! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:16'!patrol  "Retorna un patrol"  ^ patrol! !!PatrolCouple methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:36'!doTheRegularPatrol  "Los guardias repiten regularPatrol 5 veces, pero luego de cada una se corren  5 hacia el este. Considere usar bateria con suficiente carga"  5 timesRepeat: [    (self patrol canDoRegularPatrol) & (self sniper battery charge >= 9)      ifTrue: [ self patrol north. self regularPatrol ]  ]! !"-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- "!PatrolCouple class	instanceVariableNames: ''!!PatrolCouple class commentStamp: '<historical>' prior: 0!!!PatrolCouple class methodsFor: 'initialiaze' stamp: 'IvanKarl 10/2/2014 15:18'!newWithPatrol: aPatrol andSniper: aSniper  "Crea e inicializa un PatrolCouple con robots."  ^ self new patrol: aPatrol sniper: aSniper! !